{"word":"G2233 - ἡγέομαι - hēgéomai - hayg-eh'-om-ahee - Account","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἡγέομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">hēgéomai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hayg-eh'-om-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Account</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - ஆளு, நடத்து"},{"paragraph":"to lead, to rule, command; to have authority over"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Middle voice of a (presumed) strengthened form of <a href=\"#/G71 - ἄγω - ágō - ag'-o/71\">G71</a>; to <i>lead</i>, that is, <i>command</i> (with official authority); figuratively to <i>deem</i>, that is, <i>consider:</i> - account, (be) chief, count, esteem, governor, judge, have the rule over, suppose, think.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1335/1335\">G1335</a>, <a href=\"#/G1834/1834\">G1834</a>, <a href=\"#/G2233/2233\">G2233</a>, <a href=\"#/G4285/4285\">G4285</a>"}]}